CM_ SG_ 3221225472 Actual_DCCurrent "DC Current: Current on DC side. The sign of this value represents whether the motor is running(positive) current or regenerating (negative) current.";
CM_ SG_ 3221225472 Actual_ERPM "Electrical RPM
Equation: ERPM = Motor RPM * number of the motor pole pairs.";
CM_ SG_ 3221225472 Actual_Duty "The controller duty cycle. The sign of this value will represent whether the motor is running(positive) current or regenerating (negative) current.";
